name: SoundAlerter 3.3.5a
body: SoundAlerter is a World of Warcraft addon that alerts the player of enemy casted spells via voice alert, credits go to the authors of the addon GladiatorlosSA for the concept, codebase and sounds. Continued development by Trolollolol - Ragnaros - www.molten-wow.com
